option.value: Removed duplicate package event. Updated references.

MESSAGE.value: Removed the unused ModuleStack. Updated the Model to fix a type mismatch. Removed filters from the interface. Updated the view to draw the entire model - always.
Renamed ModuleLoader to ClassLoader to make it more generic. Updated ClassLoader to load objects and not classes.

Implemented a new interface for the modules called ModuleInterface. Re-designed the interfaces so both the ModuleInterface and Siigna inherit from the common trait Interface, to add more flexibility. Removed the ability to add components to interfaces. Redesigned a few things in the View and the applet. Cleared up some code here and there. Added "defaultScreenSize" to the preferences.
Removed duplicate package event. Updated references.
